         Since the exp changes went live I've been killing the revenants. </P><P>Solo'ing them isn't very hard. Their resists are iffy. 1 of 5 epic resists, 1 of 3 splurts, 1 of 5 FP, 1 of 5 roots. All in all, not too difficult. </P><P>Their HP make them rather lengthy kills but it's nothing you shouldn't be able to handle. I think it takes me 3-4 epics, 3 FPs, 2-3 Splurts, and random Vex's/ToN's to kill one.</P><P>With 100% in AA Exp they give 2% per kill, with the occasional one giving 3%.</P><P>I started off duo'ing them with a Paladin, which was incredibly incredibly easy. Pull with epic, slow, splurt, send pet, Zevfeer's every now and then when Pally needs some health.</P><P>Mordicai Nar`Zhul<BR>Warlock of The Rathe<BR>Noble Blade<BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
