         they do not summon.  I personaly don't use a spec (not that I have it).  I just charm a snaky, root the rev. slow it, and make it meet snaky.</P><P>are you sure ya want snaky?</P><P>oh yea I want snaky.</P><P>well ok, here comes snaky.</P><P><center><b>Bringer of Darkness</b><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=11832" target="_blank"><img src="http://members.cox.net/umbrae/pic.jpg" border=0></a><BR><a href="http://members.cox.net/umbrae/topless.jpg" target="_blank">Signature Pic R</a></center><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td bgcolor="black" valign="top">

		<a href="pop_profile.asp?mode=display&amp;id=3369">
	
